title: O'Funk'illo Discography
description:
O'Funk'Illo

Funk/Rock band from Spain, started on 1997. Awesome bass, funky guitar licks and solos, tight drumming and catchy tunes and lyrics.

Andreas Lutz (vocal)
Javi Marssiano (guitar)
Pepe Bao (drums)
